Top Recipe Portal- to find best recipes
=======================================

It is a crowd sourced website that allows you to add links to your favorite recipes and rate them. 

This project uses java play as the technology stack. It has used spring for dependency injection, JPA/ Hibernate for data access. The Web Interface is inspired by Pinterest. User can enter url of their favorite recipe, select image and/or video from the page. This image and/or video is used to display tiled list of recipes. Twitter bootstarp has been used for UI development.




